'''Cornelius Tennyson Daniel Marivate''' (''[[?? - ?? - ??]]''), i phurofesa loyi a yeke eku wiseni wa le Yunivhesithi ya Afrika-Dzonga(UNISA). A a ri eka Ndzawulo yaTindzimi ta Vantima laha a dyondziseke machudeni ya Xitsonga lava a va dyondza ririmi leri eYunivhesithi. U kandziyisile ntlangu wo koma wa Jim Xilovekelo hi lembe ra 1965, loko a ha ri muleteri wa Xitsonga eUNISA.<ref name=ph1>"[https://www.yumpu.com/sw/document/view/14913176/here-national-library-of-south-africa/17 Preserving and Celebrating our literary heritage]" (March 2011) - '''National Library of South Africa'''. Retrieved 22 February 2016</ref>

